block content
  .section.black_background
    .section-item.text-left
      .container
        .row.align-items-end.mt50
          .col-sm-8.mb90
            h3.section-item-title-xs about us
            h1.h2-flash.font-abril.mb-0.
              
              A Digital Revolution in Textile Market by Zero-Waste Technology
              
            hr
            h2 Backed by a Decentralized Circular Economy
            .fs18.text-grey.
              
              The engineering pilot plant comprises prototyping module machinery able to test small sizes of local high-standard raw materials to be subjected to natural dyeing technology by offering dynamic data related to treatment, analysis and conservation of water wastes.
              
          .col-sm-4.mb90
            .rounded-logo
              img(src='./img/Logo.ico/android-icon-192x192.png' alt='logo')
        .row
          .col-lg-10
            blockquote.blockquote.blockquote-status.text-left.mt-3.mb-0
              .font-libre.
                
                Naturaldyer OÜ is focused on digitizing textile manufacturing processes by developing natural dyeing technology related to an intelligent application dedicated to digital weaving procedures. We offer online mass personalization of biodegradable textiles by collecting available products and services provided by spinner-mills and weaving facilities to be activated on a digital customizer to manage personalized order reports on small and flexible quantities fabrics. The method works on defined warp-chains to be shared with online business users who demand access to the market by evaluating new yarns and colours to add brand value.
                
              footer
                strong.fs18.text-black Massimilliano Merlicco,
                br
                | Founder & CEO at Naturaldyers

    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-8
          h2.h2-flash.font-abril.mb60.mt80.
            
            Territorial Harvesting areas
            
    .section-item
      .container-fluid
        .image.mask-skew.wow.fadeIn(data-wow-offset='150' data-wow-duration='0.2s' data-wow-delay='.3s')
          .mask.wow.slideInLeft(data-wow-offset='150' data-wow-duration='1.2s' data-wow-delay='.3s')
            .inside
          img.img-fluid(src='img/pic156.jpg' alt)
    .container.mt55
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          p.fs18.
            
            The territorial pilot plants is offered by loan for use to local farmers interested in transformation procedures of Linerian fibres, native wools and natural pigments obtained by various matrices such as officinalis plants, medical herbs, algae and mushrooms directly on the field.
            
    .section-item.text-left
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-8
            h3.section-item-title-xs.mt150 Our Mission
            h1.h2-flash.font-abril.
              
              We are passionate about textile & technology.
              
        .row.horizontal-service-list
          .col-lg-4
            .horizontal-service-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='.2s')
              .num 1.
              .horizontal-service-item-photo
                img.photo-position(src='img/horizontal-pic2.png' alt)
              .horizontal-service-item-title.
                
                Digital hub
                
              .horizontal-service-item-descr.text-grey.
                
                The information technology instrument works as online estimator to provide personalized fabrics order reports by offering tested demonstrative samples for access to a reserved dashboard able to upgrade the digital tool of components such as new customized patterns and colors to increase the variable of personalization in line with each own expenses capacity
                
              .horizontal-service-item-more
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(href='service.html')
                  | Learn more 
                  i.icon.ion-ios-arrow-right
          .col-lg-4
            .horizontal-service-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='.4s')
              .num 2.
              .horizontal-service-item-photo
                img.photo-position(src='img/horizontal-pic3.png' alt)
              .horizontal-service-item-title.
                
                Mass-personalization
                
              .horizontal-service-item-descr.text-grey.
                
                The software is integrated with a virtual sales area where Designers can personalize flexible quantities of fabrics to be used prototyping unique and exclusive lead products to be offered to chromatic mass-personalization by connecting with professional retailers and consumers.
                
              .horizontal-service-item-more
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(href='service.html')
                  | Learn more 
                  i.icon.ion-ios-arrow-right
          .col-lg-4
            .horizontal-service-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='.6s')
              .num 3.
              .horizontal-service-item-photo.photo3
                img.photo-position(src='img/horizontal-pic4.png' alt)
              .horizontal-service-item-title.
                
                Smart Application
                
              .horizontal-service-item-descr.text-grey.
                
                The DIGITAL HUB services is integrated with territorial pilot plant to collect local high-standard raw materials to be standardized by registered supply-chain in order to connect Farmers in a global Brand identity able to share profits directly generated by online users for divulging dynamic data related to an innovative Zero Waste solution to the textile market.
                
              .horizontal-service-item-more
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm(href='service.html')
                  | Learn more 
                  i.icon.ion-ios-arrow-right
    .section-item.text-left
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-8
            h3.section-item-title-xs Zero waste technology
            h1.h2-flash.font-abril.mb30 Decentralized circular Bio-economy
            ul.p-0.mt5
              li The linear economy is traditionally managed on high margins generated by pollutive standardized end-products.
              li.mt10.
                
                Our innovative circular economy model is based on the tokenization of digital services dedicated to the textile value-chain interested in participating in the profits generated by online sales volume.
                
